description:
In this video, I'm going to Gordon Ramsay's Fish and Chips at the Linq Promenade! I'll give you my honest review of the fish and chips as well as the Sticky Toffee Shake! Be sure to check out my other videos reviewing Gordan Ramsay's restaurants here in Las Vegas!

Thank you for watching! Please like, share and subscribe!

Gordon Ramsay's Fish and Chips
(A): 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
(P): (702) 322-0529

Filmed on a Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra
Audio by RODE Wireless Go 2
Music from Epidemic Sound
Edited with Wondershare Filmora 11 Information regarding hours, offerings, and prices in this video are subject to change at the discretion of restaurant operators.
